{"tid":999825,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"DC9逆線行屯公　險撞迎頭車","createTime":"2019-01-29T04:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T12:05:14.000Z","uid":225464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e82b2da85cb2e420dcc14de310e7b204df9b9035","tid":999825,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>的士逆線行屯公　險撞迎頭車　網民：馬路核彈</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190129/bkn-20190129114812726-0129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190129%2Fbkn-20190129114812726-0129_00822_001.html&d=kLXyKWzv0KFRbXtH0eH7azANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=1d474601\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190129/bkn-20190129114812726-0129_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190129/photo/bkn-20190129114812726-0129_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190129120924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190129114812726-0129_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190129120924&h=407093dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪凌晨太眼瞓？<br />\n<br />\n意外是無處不在。近日有司機在屯門公路行駛時，驚見一輛逆線新界的士擦身而過，令他大驚失色。<br />\n<br />\n影片於周一（28日）上載至Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」，只見當日凌晨近4時，有司機在屯門公路近市中心位置往元朗方向行駛，誰知他正準備切往鄰線之際，一輛綠的竟突然迎面駛至。<br />\n<br />\n司機頓時驚呼：「嘩！X呀！咁都得嘅？」事後更慨嘆遇上「馬路核彈」︰「逆線亡命綠的，如入無人之境，隨時搞出人命。的士大佬咪搵啲咁嘅嘢玩」。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛斥責綠的：「隨時撞死其他司機」、「仲要有乘客，一定嚇到X縮」、「諗唔到邊個位轉入嚟」。"},{"pid":"d4854bbe1b738db0148e7041a158b0f9a1e976cc","tid":999825,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"行錯路啫"},{"pid":"bcb00f17cbae741c7279553460c6983f0a503015","tid":999825,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"GTA 日常<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}